Package: poco
Type: Package
Title: R Functions for Sample Size and Probability Calculations for the assessment of consistency in multi-regional trials
Version: 1.0
Date: 2014-03-04
Author: Andreas Kitsche
Maintainer: Andreas Kitsche <kitsche@biostat.uni-hannover.de>
Description: This package summarizes the function presented in the article "R Functions for Sample Size and Probability Calculations for Assessing Consistency of Treatment Efects in Multi-Regional Clinical Trials" by Li et al. in the Journal of Statistical Software 
Depends: mvtnorm, mratios, multcomp
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests: knitr
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes
License: GPL
